"feed_specific": {"answer_count": 84}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待「全球最顶级的鱼子酱在中国」，还有哪些你以为是外国美食其实是在中国盛产？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "提起国际顶级的生鲜食材，在很多人刻板印象中都是「国外的好」，但近日上映的纪录片《上新吧！山川湖海》中，提及了诸多国外的「网红」生鲜，如俄罗斯鱼子酱、日本正宗鳗鱼、地中海甘露，其实「中国制造」已经达到了相当的品质，甚至更好。你还知道哪些外国特有美食，而其实是在中国盛产？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-4837dd52c85891bf7feff1d37a74010b_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "485 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/497763975"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IkLPWurKz265CEAMaCDcyODk1NjYwIKyuqYwGMBs47gRABHIJNDk3NzYzOTc1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1636610593.8599443", "card_id": "Q_497148092", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 232}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么感觉今年 EDG 夺冠庆祝的声量比当年 iG 首冠还要大？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "当年 ig 夺冠，大家也就在楼里喊喊 IG 牛逼，今年却有很多人拿着 edg 的队旗在庆祝，为什么，仅看到我们学校是这样，IG 还是第一个冠军"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-f6a51f387686153c6af3920f1edef96a_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "470 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/497148092"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIkLPWurKz265CEAMaCDcyNzU4NTkxILyEm4wGMBM41QJABXIJNDk3MTQ4MDkyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1636610593.8604035", "card_id": "Q_360900500", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 474}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么 LoL 新手越来越少了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": " "}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-7b1693ceb9ffe1fcf9d786203aae2b17_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "455 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/360900500"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIkLPWurKz2